This game takes place 18 months after The Black Gate
Batlin, the leader of the Fellowship has disappeared, as well as Iolo's wife Gwenno
A map is found that points to the Serpent Isle where the Guardian is still planning to destroy Britannia
Lord British sends you, the Avatar, and your companions to this new land
Once there, you discover that a great imbalance is upon the isle and it is up to you to fix it
To do so, you must learn the philosophies of the original inhabitants of this land who worshipped giant serpents symbolizing the principles of Order, Chaos and Balance.